{"tid":1810830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"零售銷售十連跌 年挫近24%","createTime":"2020-01-04T07:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:51:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b6a84f2101441d729145fc1fbc3e0e3495bb9b","tid":1810830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:48:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200104/MSYP2RG7BOTC5B4YRRH4KOFYHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200104%2FMSYP2RG7BOTC5B4YRRH4KOFYHE%2F&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=75be8564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200104%2FMSYP2RG7BOTC5B4YRRH4KOFYHE%2F&h=97bbc2b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200104/MSYP2RG7BOTC5B4YRRH4KOFYHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n零售銷售十連跌 年挫近24%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200104/large/1578068711_f352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200104%2Flarge%2F1578068711_f352.jpg&h=a123e7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府統計處公佈，去年11月零售總銷貨值臨時估計為300億元，按年大跌23.6%兼連挫10個月。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自由行人數大減，本地居民消費意欲低，零售數據續插水。統計處公佈去年11月零售總銷貨值臨時估計為300億元，按年跌23.6%兼連挫10個月，但較10月的24.3%跌幅略為改善。政府發言人稱社會事件「變得極度暴力」，對旅遊及消費構成嚴重干擾；業界則估計，反映聖誕及新年市道的12月零售數字會有輕微改善。<br />\n<br />\n扣除其間價格變動，去年11月零售業總銷貨數量臨時估計按年跌25.4%，而總結去年首11個月，零售業總銷貨價值合計臨時估計跌10.3%。按零售商分類，仍以珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物表現最差，11月銷貨值按年續跌43.5%；其次為藥物及化妝品，銷貨值挫33.4%；百貨公司貨品銷貨值亦插32.9%。超市貨品銷貨值則逆市升2.6%，燃料銷貨值大漲11.2%。<br />\n傳LV關時代廣場分店<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人指，零售業前景取決社會事件如何發展，對零售業及經濟復蘇至為重要。<br />\n<br />\n零售管理協會主席謝邱安儀認為市道仍不明朗，主因高基數效應及社運未完，但引述業界預測，12月銷售跌幅會收窄數個百分點。對於有報道指，法國奢侈品牌路易威登（LV）因業主九倉置業（1997）不願減租，加上生意轉差，計劃關閉銅鑼灣時代廣場分店，謝邱安儀相信農曆新年過後，結業及裁員潮將更明顯。"},{"pid":"8d37ae941d7bb26c189557847264adf78ba66409","tid":1810830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月5日 星期日<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">新春上水和你行</span><br />\n時間 ： 1500<br />\n地點:上水一號花園(龍豐對面)-&gt;上水黨鐵站C出口<br />\n活動TG頻道：<a href=\"https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwedontlikegreygoodstrader&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=44d7c909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wedontlikegreygoodstrader</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">（已獲不反對通知書）</span><br />\n<br />\n==============<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">銅鑼灣 x 灣仔稅局 和你Lunch</span><br />\n日期：2020年1月6日 星期一<br />\n時間 ： 1245 <br />\n地點 ：時代廣場集合/灣仔稅務局"},{"pid":"b630546e3df5f147ee5d6cf39168eef8657ae135","tid":1810830,"uid":82068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"即係證明香港地唔洗咁多零售囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6dabe762c0825391a94a6a82f673caa2930b933","tid":1810830,"uid":158457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"攬炒GoGoGo<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfiSOUE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfiSOUE.gif&h=65a54900&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44db83d2988fcf3d6993fc05887d953b7dc8bbeb","tid":1810830,"uid":56023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"仍以珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物表現最差，11月銷貨值按年續跌43.5%<br />\n<br />\n開咁多俾蝗 快啲執撚晒佢回復生態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d72171464e298d8e34c66fdb3a695dede5eda32","tid":1810830,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4bd580d1c30c5c7